    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Holotype of Kalophrynus honbaensis sp. nov. (ZMMU A- 4941) in preservative: (A) dorsal view, (B) ventral view, (C) profile view. Scale bar 3 mm. Photo by V. Trounov." ;
